Took me a while to finish this one. The core idea wasn't really sustained by the object itself, so I decided to do a format-skew and frame a very simple SCP in a very different world. That is the past.

Thanks to Golden506 for help in the forums.

I'm hoping to make more of these, that is, articles from this time period. My overall goal would be to create a hub full of these  documents from the Foundation at around the early 1900s. If anyone else would be willing to help and take this further, feel free to contact me. I'd love to go that step further and make a canon if anyone is willing to help.







